'''Motufala''' is an [[islet]] of the [[Nukunonu]] island group of [[Tokelau]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.janeresture.com/tokelau_islands/nukunonu.htm |title=Nukunonu Island, Tokelau |accessdate=2015-06-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nzetc.victoria.ac.nz/tm/scholarly/tei-MacToke-t1-body-d1-d1.html |title=Introduction - NZETC |accessdate=2015-06-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nzetc.victoria.ac.nz/tm/scholarly/tei-MacToke-t1-body-d1-d1-d3.html |title=Geography - NZETC |accessdate=2015-06-21}}</ref>

